    "ArticleTitle": "Loop-mediated isothermal amplification (LAMP): An effective molecular point-of-care technique for the rapid diagnosis of coronavirus SARS-CoV-2.",
    "Pagination": {
      "StartPage": "e2215",
      "MedlinePgn": "e2215"
